Bottler
=======
Simple irc bot made in C.

Features
--------
* Basic commands (!h help, !v version, !o owner, !j join, !p part)
* Fetch URL titles
* Autoreconnect (with bottler-autoreconnect)
* Autojoin

Configuration
-------------
Configuration is done by editing config.h and rebuilding
or by command-line arguments.

Example config.h:
// server hostname
char *host = "irc.quakenet.org";

// server port
char *port = "6667";

// bot nickname
char *nick = "bottler";

// bot username
char *name = "bottler irc bot";

// bot owner
char *owner = "~causes@8.28.87.203";

// autojoin channels
char *channels = "#channel #another #third";
